description:
Christina Aguchi is the first wrestler from a rival wrestling sit to get on the US mat. Her record on our shoot date was 2-1. The Tsunami comes with about 120 minutes of actual mat experience. If you compare that with US that is about 5 matches. However we know that experience on one mat is not the same as experience on our mat.
Vendetta is ranked 2nd. Her only lost last season was to the Nightmare by 1pt. Make no mistake Vendetta wants the over all title this year!
title: Vendetta (8-3) Ranked 2th
